34
00:03:42,681 --> 00:03:46,313
I know she can't replace
Bobby Kimball, but ...

35
00:03:46,868 --> 00:03:50,523
if you get along with her,
she could do Bobby's work.

36
00:03:51,231 --> 00:03:55,293
