No more appointments this week, right?

39
00:04:05,871 --> 00:04:08,207
The computer says ...

40
00:04:08,290 --> 00:04:10,009
No ...

41
00:04:10,292 --> 00:04:13,220
I gotta go check on
something.  I'll be right back.

42
00:04:13,545 --> 00:04:17,657
