Morning, folks.  I'm Gerald Tovar,
your new Funeral Director.

87
00:09:31,071 --> 00:09:33,666
Francis Del Amo.

88
00:09:33,991 --> 00:09:37,264
- My wife, Honey.
- Well, that's a sweet name.

89
00:09:38,537 --> 00:09:42,583
