- How are you folks this morning?

90
00:09:44,668 --> 00:09:47,379
Can't complain.

91
00:09:51,425 --> 00:09:54,612
I'm sorry.  There's
no smoking in here.

92
00:09:56,060 --> 00:09:56,949
Right.

93
00:09:57,184 --> 00:10:00,252
So, what can Tovar & Son
Mortuary do for you?

94
00:10:01,668 --> 00:10:06,298
